--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
THIRD-PARTY MODEL CHECKPOINTS

This package bundles the following pre-trained model checkpoints under
tako_ci/assets/. Each is the property of its respective authors and is governed
by that model's own upstream license and citation requirements:

  - skala-1.1        (Skala exchange-correlation functional)
  - nequix-mp-1      (Nequix, Materials Project training set)
  - nequix-mp-1-pft
  - nequip-s         (NequIP)

Consult the upstream projects for the terms that apply to each checkpoint before
redistribution or commercial use. The compiled WASM cores (mlip_core, qc_core)
are build artifacts of the Tako calculation engines.
